channel.title: IP Problems
channel.description: I have a PhoneScape server working and running, and I'm on it, and as i'm about to register the server I see I need to type in an IP. Where can I find this IP, because when I tried to make another one, MoparScape just said to click "Start Server," when I know that makes a HybridScape server. How do I find this IP?
